Features:
	- Play a two player game of chess!
	- Be able to save the state of the chess game at any point.
	- Be able to connect and play a game over the network.


Play a game of chess.

Detect saved game and load, or initialize the board for a new game. 

-Place the pieces at the correct positions. 
-Display the pieces and board

